io.github.utk003.util.math.solve

Class QuarticFormula

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.utk003.util.math.solve.QuarticFormula

  • @ScheduledForRelease(inVersion="v3.0.0")
public final class QuarticFormula
extends Object
    A quartic equation solver.

    This class provides the same functionality as class and instance methods. The instance methods use cached QuarticSolution instances to hold and return solutions to cubic equations while the class methods create new instances each time.

    This class is only for equations whose coefficients are all real. For a similar solver that works with complex coefficients, use ComplexQuarticFormula.

    Since:
    3.0.0
    Version:
    July 21, 2021
    Author:
    Utkarsh Priyam (utk003)
    See Also:
    QuarticSolution, ComplexQuarticFormula
